{"tid":961714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"晴天霹靂！2019年地球將進入迷你冰河期，周期為12年！","createTime":"2018-12-30T10:35:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T02:15:18.000Z","uid":53026,"like":13,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"b359a0cf786d34d5d61ae90008ce25932228da0d","tid":961714,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T10:35:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/science/3xqrkma.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fscience%2F3xqrkma.html&d=CRKoJJKcEYNPdDAlVu15XP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=39783176\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/science/3xqrkma.html</a><br />\n<br />\n來自(英國)諾森比亞大學的瓦倫蒂娜&middot;茲哈科娃教授領導的一個由科學家組成的研究小組的一項驚人的研究表明，地球將在未來幾年內進入一個冷卻階段。<br />\n<br />\nZharkova和她的團隊通過建立太陽磁場的數學模型得出了令人震驚的結論。<br />\n<br />\n她的發現表明，在2020年到2053年之間的33年中，太陽活動的「大幅減少」將導致全球氣溫驟降。<br />\n<br />\n她的模型預測，隨着太陽活動的減少，溫度將下降到自17世紀以來未曾見過的最低點&mdash;&mdash;這一時期被稱為蒙德極小期。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/science/3xqrkma.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fscience%2F3xqrkma.html&d=CRKoJJKcEYNPdDAlVu15XP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=39783176\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/science/3xqrkma.html</a>"},{"pid":"a426863945f2e1ae55b2aca841f7bbb25c69065a","tid":961714,"uid":10670,"like":14,"dislike":8,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T10:36:04.000Z","msg":"暖化撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fb601854bb1a1d605927cf67e3510a63851b60f","tid":961714,"uid":79627,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T10:36:05.000Z","msg":"Content farm<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0444587d4ff20d871a8860ffd0aaace1cdc6388c","tid":961714,"uid":197563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T10:40:10.000Z","msg":"英國研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />